Doetinchem

Netherlands
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Online marketing mentor.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I help business coaches to become visible online and attract clients.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
Life and business coaches want to help people. It is my mission to help these coaches to attracts clients and make more money so they can continue to do what they love. Also I love to write and publish, and interview people.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
Mind shift from independent professional to entrepreneur. Instead of finding revenue for each month to building a sustainable business.
</p>

